Source: http://gettingstartedwithchef.com/first-steps-with-chef.html

High level steps:
1. Install a Ubuntu VM.
2. Put chef-repo under /root/.
3. install chef-solo: curl -L https://www.opscode.com/chef/install.sh | bash
4. cd chef-repo/
5. chef-solo -c solo.rb -j web.json

Then you should have a working web server.
